{"tid":1913071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"平機會指貼「不為藍絲」服務等字句不涉反歧視條例","createTime":"2020-03-06T13:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T15:06:05.000Z","uid":3090,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"471544eabf4ef921aa6facb694fa01c3484aeee4","tid":1913071,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3VrqyuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VrqyuZ.jpg&h=a8356885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n平機會表示，如有任何人有疑問或懷疑受到歧視，歡迎向平機會查詢或投訴。（港台圖片）<br />\n2020-03-06 HKT 21:33<br />\n<br />\n平機會表示，有區議員於辦事處門外貼出告示，寫上「不為任何藍絲提供服務」及「藍絲與狗不得內進」的字句，並不涉及現行四條反歧視條例。<br />\n<br />\n平機會表示，如有任何人有疑問或懷疑受到歧視，歡迎向平機會查詢或投訴。<br />\n<br />\n平機會主席朱敏健表示，區議員作為公職人員，公職行為包括服務該區所有市民，理論上不應拒絕服務任何區內的市民，平機會反對任何形式的歧視行為，衷心希望社會各界能放下歧見，上下一心，團結抗疫，使香港可以盡快渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512928-20200306.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512928-20200306.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnOoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=34ab5b5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512928-20200306.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed059a07\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512928-20200306.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b0c9e63601f8882ad843af6129b8719ebf16b3be","tid":1913071,"uid":77092,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74b6a94751ff2990a5fb182cd6b157f2284dc9fe","tid":1913071,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"good<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d1baca3519498c3e998951f08285dc9b51fadfb","tid":1913071,"uid":271545,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"好明顯歧視狗隻喎"},{"pid":"002dcc9e7d1b9771e5f15d2aa0536e32c7960bf0","tid":1913071,"uid":63543,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"0d1baca3519498c3e998951f08285dc9b51fadfb","tid":1913071,"uid":271545,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"好明顯歧視狗隻喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"要加句導盲犬除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467894d4cd89635f46677e5a68dd2d427e4321e9","tid":1913071,"uid":133319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b449fe5b5682b05ac32b12614ddf6c789d9b147","tid":1913071,"uid":3241,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"呢d真係要大大力貼， 等果班少數派親支垃圾唔好係度扮自己好多人支持"},{"pid":"8583759dd2d9f583e89f1ff34fba92daa3558d85","tid":1913071,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0d1baca